metadata.name: The Phases Within
metadata.description:
This intriguing piece  "The Phases Within" depicts the subtle struggles of a man's life journey.
The sobs he can't shed, the emotions he can't publicly express, and the fake smiles he has to put on to mask his suffering.

It delves into a man's inner world, revealing the layers of complexity that lie beyond his outward appearance.

It presents an insightful analysis of masculinity and the human condition and challenges viewers to consider how cultural constraints and expectations impact his life.
